<b>
<a href="http://www.ralloszek.net/ubbthreads/showthreaded.php?Cat=&amp;Board=rp&amp;Number=2467&amp;page=0&amp;view=collapsed&amp;sb=5&amp;o=&amp;vc=1" target="_new" title="Re: to post #2467" alt="Re: to post #2467"> To Reflect on Past Injustice </a>
