<td align="left" width="70%" valign="top">
<img src="/ubbthreads/images/icons/book.gif" width="15" height="15" alt="" style="vertical-align: text-top" />
<b>
<a href="http://www.ralloszek.net/ubbthreads/showthreaded.php?Cat=&amp;Board=rp&amp;Number=3611&amp;page=0&amp;view=collapsed&amp;sb=5&amp;o=&amp;vc=1" target="_new" title="Re: to post #3611" alt="Re: to post #3611">Standing in the Breech…</a>
</b>
 <img alt="new" src="/ubbthreads/images/new.gif" />
 
<br />
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
<font class="small">
#4588 - 01/06/02 08:05 PM <i></i> 
