Dear father,<br>How many times must i try to locate you? I have been away for so long, you are nowhere to be found. I believe I may have taken a step forward by refusing to let the past take hold of me. I will miss him dearly. I have grown much since last we met father, it will be nice to see you once again. Alas, I am back.<br>Love,<br>LuLu<br><br>(ooc: yes des i found the website you were telling me about before, lulee is coming out of retirement...) <br>(ooc: i have a lot of reading to do now, i see that you and carezzy have written novels, much to my liking - as to the others on this forum -- nice to meet you all, may the stories continue~)


