<td width="83%" class="lighttable">
<br />
<font class="post">
As long as a crippeling drinking problem afflicts my life, and my IRL friends choose to ignore the roleplaying board on the site, we will have the Continued Adventures of Kelleher Ivyelm<br>Kelleher Ivyelm<br>46th Level Half Elven Ranger 


