ooc: Oh, dear.  I thought this board had been deleted after trying to find it for a few weeks.  I just sort of tossed the things I had begun, so I need to dig it out again.<br><br>Hello, Lulee!!! I am happy you are here!!  I miss you Father Des.  I do not see you in Norrath anymore.  <br><br>I shall be adding as soon as I catch up on the story. <br><br>Sir Kelleher, I always enjoy reading the things you write.....but I am sorry your real life is not going terribly well.  Good luck to you.<br><br>Carezzia  


